2.All articles amended and promulgated under Order Nung-Liang-Tze 0981047719 and Wei-Shu-Shi-Tze 0980402341 dated July 24,2009
3.Articles 4 and 11 amended under Order Nung-Liang-Tze 1001053260 and Wei-Shu-Shi-Tze 1001301669 dated June 23, 2011
